{{Quote|Cheenee Rift has more holes in it then a chunk of Byss cheese.|[[Risha Drayen]]|<ref name="TOR">{{TORcite|type=class|[[Voidhound|Smuggler]]|Bait|[[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]}}</ref>}}
Created by the [[Abyssin/Legends|Abyssin]] species, '''Byss cheese''' was a cheese noted for its large holes.
The fact its hole were so noticeable meant that similarly cratered planets and moons were referred to as Byss cheese. For example, [[Yavin 13/Legends|Yavin 13]]; the thirteenth moon of [[Yavin Prime/Legends|Yavin Prime]]. It was used in a [[Shaak and cheese sandwich]] served at [[Dex's Diner/Legends|Dex's Diner]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]<ref name="Dex">{{Hyperspace|url=fans/hyperspace/source/dexdiner/index.html|text=Dining at Dex's|int=Dining at Dex's}}</ref>

